- Sit on her legs.

06:11.667 --> 06:14.731
You're getting a thrill out of
this, aren't you, you pervert?

06:15.750 --> 06:17.374
- Oh, my God.
- What?

06:17.375 --> 06:20.624
You're Martin Sharp. You
are a pervert, officially!

06:20.625 --> 06:24.416
That's it! Rise and Shine
with Martin and Penny!

06:24.417 --> 06:26.983
Just let me go...

06:29.917 --> 06:32.318
- No, just...
- Wait!

06:37.708 --> 06:39.316
Hi.

06:40.125 --> 06:41.684
Erm...

06:42.917 --> 06:46.230
Any of you guys order a pizza?

06:48.792 --> 06:51.442
Well, shall we do introductions?

06:53.208 --> 06:55.017
I'm Jess.

06:55.333 --> 06:57.521
Everyone calls me Jess.

06:58.792 --> 07:01.193
I... I'm Maureen.

07:01.667 --> 07:04.082
- I'm, uh... I'm JJ.
- I'm...

07:04.083 --> 07:05.457
- Martin Sharp.
- Yes.

07:05.458 --> 07:08.606
It's very exciting to have a
celebrity in our suicidal midst.

07:09.167 --> 07:10.624
- This feels wrong.
- Mmm.

07:10.625 --> 07:13.607
All right, well, we could just
do a "one, two, three, jump!"

07:17.625 --> 07:19.647
Whoa!

07:23.917 --> 07:27.124
