Eve unless you're serious.

07:34.792 --> 07:36.351
Nice to meet you.

07:37.625 --> 07:41.650
It was just another
debacle. Another cock-up.

07:42.083 --> 07:44.457
I'd have believed you if you'd
told me half an hour before

07:44.458 --> 07:46.832
that I'd end up on my car,

07:46.833 --> 07:48.606
but not in it.

07:55.500 --> 07:58.582
And I absolutely knew, with
every fibre of my being,

07:58.583 --> 08:02.194
