out, thank you very much.

08:07.708 --> 08:09.814
I had no interest whatsoever.

08:14.417 --> 08:16.273
Oh, fuck.

08:16.417 --> 08:18.624
Do I regret stopping
to pick her up?

08:18.625 --> 08:22.069
Well, that really is along story.

08:25.875 --> 08:28.207
- Want a lift?
- No, no.

08:28.208 --> 08:31.735
The bus will be
along in 15 minutes.

08:31.833 --> 08:33.855
Get in the car, Maureen.

08:37.750 --> 08:39.308
Oh!

08:46.292 --> 08:48.563
I did like your television show.

09:19.917 --> 09:23.666
- What are you doing?
- Aw, it's a bit early for a reunion, isn't it?

09:23.667 --> 09:26.400
