We're taking you home.

09:37.000 --> 09:38.939
So this is...

09:40.542 --> 09:42.149
Jolly.

09:42.625 --> 09:44.398
OK.

09:44.958 --> 09:46.166
One word answers.

09:46.167 --> 09:47.749
Everyone has one word to explain

09:47.750 --> 09:49.457
why they were up on the
roof in the first place.

09:49.458 --> 09:53.435
For example, Martin might say

09:53.458 --> 09:55.541
- notoriety.
- Mmm-hmm.

09:55.542 --> 09:58.736
- Maureen might say loneliness.
- I'm not lonely.

09:58.833 --> 10:01.874
- Tell that to your cats.
- I don't have cats.

10:01.875 --> 10:04.063
I was up there because I felt...

10:04.958 --> 10:06.666
- Helpless.
- Helpless?

10:06.667 --> 10:07.916
That's a very good adjective.

10:07.917 --> 10:11.291
Are we not fitting into your
pre-ordained boxes, Jess?

10:11.292 --> 10:14.457
