one marvellously, Martin.

10:14.458 --> 10:16.480
Was prison fun?

10:16.917 --> 10:20.360
You really believe you have an
answer for everything, don't you?

10:20.750 --> 10:24.332
I really believe that you
are a miserable bastard.

10:24.333 --> 10:28.124
Actually, right now, a miserable
bastard is exactly what I am.

10:28.125 --> 10:29.981
Have I not been hiding it well?

10:30.375 --> 10:32.332
- Pizza boy.
- JJ.

10:32.333 --> 10:34.624
Why might pizza boy want to die?

10:34.625 --> 10:37.541
What would be your reason, Jess?

10:37.542 --> 10:40.624
My reason would be love.

10:40.625 --> 10:44.082
Chas. Chas the dickhead.
He spurned me.

10:44.083 --> 10:45.986
I'm a spurned woman.

10:46.542 --> 10:48.149
Cancer.

10:49.500 --> 10:52.731
I was up there
because I have cancer.

10:53.167 --> 10:55.249
I have inoperable cancer.

10:55.250 --> 10:57.332
We have a winner.

10:57.333 --> 10:58.916
That's fucking brilliant.

10:58.917 --> 11:02.041
Very impressed. Is it
an embarrassing cancer?

11:02.042 --> 11:03.649
Brain.

11:04.333 --> 11:06.023
CCR.

11:06.250 --> 11:08.707
- I'm sorry, JJ.
- Yeah.

11:08.708 --> 11:10.944
I think colon would
have been better.

11:12.000 --> 11:13.807
Ooh, we're here.

11:17.875 --> 11:21.603
What, here? You live here?

11:21.792 --> 11:24.624
No, but Chas is likely to be here

11:24.625 --> 11:27.986
and I've got a couple of
things I want to say to him.

11:29.958 --> 11:32.457
Good luck with your next
attempt. See you in the afterlife.

11:32.458 --> 11:34.066
Yep, good night.

11:50.000 --> 11:52.235
Unhappy little thing, isn't she?

11:53.083 --> 11:54.986
