11:55.667 --> 11:57.999
The most popular place
in London for suicides

11:58.000 --> 12:00.416
on the most popular
night for suicides.

12:00.417 --> 12:01.999
I should have known.

12:02.000 --> 12:05.332
- I wouldn't be alone.
- I don't know why she thought I have cats.

12:05.333 --> 12:08.647
And she certainly
swears too much, but...

12:11.542 --> 12:13.707
Go on, Maureen, just say it.

12:13.708 --> 12:16.145
I just, um...

12:17.667 --> 12:19.605
Should she be alone?

12:35.292 --> 12:36.499
Right.

12:36.500 --> 12:39.624
Uh, Martin, you,
uh, you go that way.

12:39.625 --> 12:41.541
- I'll go... I'll go this way.
- No, no, no. I can't do this...

12:41.542 --> 12:44.416
What else are we gonna do?
Hey, what else are we gonna do?

12:44.417 --> 12:46.041
And, Maureen, uh...

12:46.042 --> 12:48.124
You take... You take the bathrooms.

12:48.125 --> 12:50.894
The bathrooms. Bathrooms? OK, go.

12:57.542 --> 13:00.559
I'm looking for a
girl called Jess. Jess?

13:07.417 --> 13:11.193
I'm looking... I'm looking
for a girl called Jess. Jess?

13:35.875 --> 13:40.480
- Hi. I'm looking for a...
- Hi.

13:41.333 --> 13:43.320
- I'm looking for a...
- Hi.

13:43.625 --> 13:47.436
I'm looking for a girl... Jess.

13:55.750 --> 13:57.249
Good.

13:57.250 --> 14:00.315
Great. Perfect.

14:02.625 --> 14:05.416
17, 16,

14:05.417 --> 14:08.332
15,14.

14:08.333 --> 14:11.249
13,12.

14:11.250 --> 14:13.707
11,10.

14:13.708 --> 14:15.916
Nine, eight,

14:15.917 --> 14:18.166
seven, six,

14:18.167 --> 14:20.249
five, four,

14:20.250 --> 14:23.207
three, two, one!

14:23.208 --> 14:25.942
Happy New Year!

14:55.083 --> 14:58.101
- Hi.
- Uh...

14:58.292 --> 15:01.060
- You hiding, too, are you?
- Yeah.

15:01.208 --> 15:03.124
I've... I've taken some pills.

15:03.125 --> 15:05.064
It's all good.

15:05.667 --> 15:08.566
- What are you hiding from?
- Oh, you know...

15:09.208 --> 15:12.207
Humans. Humanity, life. You?

15:12.208 --> 15:13.874
The nutter who's trying to kill me.

15:13.875 --> 15:15.874
Your reason's better
