15:57.875 --> 16:00.166
- OK.
- Just let me leave quietly.

16:00.167 --> 16:03.166
- All right. OK.
- I've done nothing wrong.

16:03.167 --> 16:04.374
Nothing wrong?

16:04.375 --> 16:07.653
Taking her to bed! Nothing wrong?

16:07.667 --> 16:10.332
Where is she? Where's
