16:22.167 --> 16:23.999
- Preparing to...
- What?

16:24.000 --> 16:27.895
Hey! Hey, it's Jess. Come on.

16:29.125 --> 16:30.666
- How's she doing?
- Ready?

16:30.667 --> 16:32.666
- Hey, Jess.
