16:37.917 --> 16:40.999
- I need to know her name.
- I only, uh... She's called Jess.

16:41.000 --> 16:44.374
- Sir, I need her full name.
- None of us knew her before tonight.

16:44.375 --> 16:46.314
You need to wait here.

16:47.083 --> 16:50.978
- She's got no identification on her, no nothing.
- Yeah, well,

16:51.000 --> 16:53.374
