by taking pills.

19:05.208 --> 19:07.707
I'd probably do
something really cool,

19:07.708 --> 19:10.986
like jumping off the
top of a tower block.

19:11.333 --> 19:13.439
Jess, we were worried.

19:13.583 --> 19:15.541
Was I on number three? Erm...

19:15.542 --> 19:18.939
I think I was on number
four. I just wanted to say,

19:19.208 --> 19:21.416
thank you so much for caring,

19:21.417 --> 19:24.374
because I really, um... I
really, really appreciate it.

19:24.375 --> 19:28.151
