going to live to regret this.

22:11.833 --> 22:14.400
Guys, look.

22:17.792 --> 22:20.276
So, this is a new year, then.

22:22.042 --> 22:24.893
Yeah.

22:28.625 --> 22:31.374
Hang on. Maureen, just
a fucking question here.

22:31.375 --> 22:33.124
Have we just written our
pact on the back of your

22:33.125 --> 22:35.147
- suicide note?
- Oh...

22:35.667 --> 22:37.653
