and I'm trying to protect you.

25:14.208 --> 25:18.332
Oh, yeah. Well, you've always been
really great at that, haven't you?

25:18.333 --> 25:21.207
- Jess...
- What the hell are you doing here?

25:21.208 --> 25:22.416
Uh...

25:22.417 --> 25:24.707
- I was invited.
- You were invited?

25:24.708 --> 25:27.166
Politician's daughter.
I was surprised.

25:27.167 --> 25:28.749
I called his agent. I
thought we should all talk.

25:28.750 --> 25:29.999
- You called his agent?
- Yeah.

25:30.000 --> 25:31.624
He was delighted.

25:31.625 --> 25:34.061
First call he'd had in awhile.

25:34.625 --> 25:37.166
Was it you... Who
went to the press?

25:37.167 --> 25:38.457
No!

25:38.458 --> 25:40.624
I've been trying to figure
