25:40.625 --> 25:41.916
JJ?

25:41.917 --> 25:43.541
He's too shy.

25:43.542 --> 25:45.249
It's not Maureen.

25:45.250 --> 25:46.976
No, no.

25:47.333 --> 25:49.791
Hey, it was fucking Chas.

25:49.792 --> 25:51.416
Chas sold us.

25:51.417 --> 25:55.166
My ex-wife rang this morning,
wanting to know what I'd done.

25:55.167 --> 25:56.957
Asking me what she
should tell the children.

25:56.958 --> 25:58.124
Oh, I'm gonna fucking kill him.

25:58.125 --> 26:00.624
She told me I seem to be the
only person in the whole world

26:00.625 --> 26:02.332
