27:19.250 --> 27:20.832
- All right.
- Yep.

27:20.833 --> 27:23.082
Yep. Good luck.

27:23.083 --> 27:24.691
Yep.

27:40.583 --> 27:43.582
This is the second tragedy
for the Crichton family

27:43.583 --> 27:47.791
after the disappearance of older
sister, Jennifer two years ago.

27:47.792 --> 27:50.707
Jennifer was never found,
and you have to wonder

27:50.708 --> 27:54.124
