they can provide, it's better.

30:55.542 --> 30:57.207
And I don't hide him.

30:57.208 --> 30:59.314
I've never hidden him, never.

30:59.542 --> 31:02.207
Can we get back to the
matter in hand, hmm?

31:02.208 --> 31:05.499
Yeah, we're all here to
figure out how to get them to

31:05.500 --> 31:07.249
