live, where Maureen lives.

31:26.500 --> 31:28.541
- What, they'll be here?
- So, I've been...

31:28.542 --> 31:30.445
I've been thinking.

31:30.500 --> 31:33.666
What if we shift the goal posts?

31:33.667 --> 31:36.082
- Goal posts?
- Yeah, make it our story, not theirs.

31:36.083 --> 31:39.832
I mean, there's even the possibility
that we might be able to make some

31:39.833 --> 31:41.249
money out of it.

31:41.250 --> 31:42.624
- Money?
- Yeah, money.

31:42.625 --> 31:44.166
That would be good
for Matty, wouldn't it?

31:44.167 --> 31:46.791
I'm sure JJ would like
a break from pizzas.

31:46.792 --> 31:48.916
And as an unemployed,
disgraced talk show host,

31:48.917 --> 31:50.207
I could certainly do with it.

31:50.208 --> 31:52.249
I don't... I don't want
Matty in the papers.

31:52.250 --> 31:54.568
We... We can't stop that.

31:55.500 --> 32:00.582
But, at least, this way
we won't lose out entirely.

32:00.583 --> 32:02.457
By telling our story...

32:02.458 --> 32:04.527
What... What story?

32:04.542 --> 32:07.291
That we went up, then
we came back down again.

32:07.292 --> 32:10.041
They've sold newspapers
off our backs.

32:10.042 --> 32:13.439
- Isn't it time we got something out of it?
- I...

32:16.208 --> 32:19.666
- Yes, OK.
- Good. Great.

32:19.667 --> 32:21.356
Yeah?

32:21.500 --> 32:24.082
- Well?
- Yeah, I mean, if you think it's...

32:24.083 --> 32:26.249
If you think it's right,
Martin, yeah, I'm in.

32:26.250 --> 32:27.791
I mean, I'm fine financially,

32:27.792 --> 32:29.999
'cos, you know, I've
got my dad to nick from.

32:30.000 --> 32:31.607
Oh.

32:31.667 --> 32:37.232
But if we were to make
the story a fun one...

32:53.625 --> 32:55.207
