shalt not die tonight."

33:41.750 --> 33:43.749
I mean, this is Matt
Damon, the naked angel.

33:43.750 --> 33:46.791
- What?
- Maybe we shouldn't write all of this down.

33:46.792 --> 33:49.749
Can I talk to your editor?
Used to be a good mate of mine.

33:49.750 --> 33:51.736
Oh, an actor.

33:52.250 --> 33:53.457
What films has he been in?

33:53.458 --> 33:55.624
You're not actually
gonna print this, are you?

33:55.625 --> 33:58.607
Yeah. Yeah, no, that's how it went.

34:02.917 --> 34:05.318
I had an interesting
thing happen today.

34:05.625 --> 34:08.275
- Did you?
- Let me guess.

34:08.292 --> 34:12.731
Your second daughter humiliated you
on the pages of the national press?

34:14.708 --> 34:17.623
Actually, no. I was
in the Members' Bar...

34:17.625 --> 34:19.123
And somebody came up
to you and they said,

34:19.125 --> 34:24.891
"Chris, was that your daughter on
the pages of the national press?"

34:25.542 --> 34:28.206
People have laughed
at me for a long time,

34:28.208 --> 34:32.980
but I did prefer it when
they didn't laugh at you.

34:35.583 --> 34:37.485
An angel.

34:37.750 --> 34:41.041
You told them you saw an angel.

34:41.042 --> 34:43.623
- Chris.
- And did it look like Jennifer?

34:43.625 --> 34:45.694
Is that what you were going to say?

34:48.083 --> 34:49.643
No.

34:52.375 --> 34:54.728
No, Dad, I...

34:54.917 --> 34:57.483
I didn't tell them it
looked like Jennifer.

35:02.583 --> 35:05.482
I told them that it
looked like Matt Damon.

35:07.125 --> 35:08.749
Zoom in on camera two.

35:08.750 --> 35:12.277
Penny, you're on
in three, two, one.

35:12.625 --> 35:17.041
Many of us have been transfixed by
the story of the Topper House Four

35:17.042 --> 35:19.582
and the angel that visited them.

35:19.583 --> 35:22.124
And we are so lucky here
on Rise and Shine with Penny

35:22.125 --> 35:24.124
to have them with us
in the studio today.

35:24.125 --> 35:26.707
One of them certainly needs
no introduction. Martin.

35:26.708 --> 35:28.957
Martin Sharp, my old co-host.

35:28.958 --> 35:32.207
Penny, it's an honour to be back
on this old sofa again with you.

35:32.208 --> 35:34.207
And I'd really like to
take this opportunity

35:34.208 --> 35:37.666
to correct a few misconceptions
about this so-called angel...

35:37.667 --> 35:39.957
