have time for that, Martin,

35:39.958 --> 35:42.457
but it would be remiss of
me not to begin the interview

35:42.458 --> 35:44.416
with a bit of background
on what's been happening

35:44.417 --> 35:46.485
to you in the last 12 months.

35:48.833 --> 35:50.416
Yes, well, um...

35:50.417 --> 35:53.957
Yes, well, Penny, currently I'm
juggling various job opportunities,

35:53.958 --> 35:56.276
concentrating on being a father.

35:56.500 --> 35:58.832
And, before that, I was in prison.

35:58.833 --> 36:01.291
But what we'd actually
like to talk to you about

36:01.292 --> 36:03.499
