you to suicidal feelings.

36:21.042 --> 36:22.207
That's right, Penny.

36:22.208 --> 36:25.191
Which is, of course, where...

36:25.542 --> 36:27.416
Where he met you lovely people.

36:27.417 --> 36:30.082
Yeah. Yeah, we, er...
We all met up there.

36:30.083 --> 36:33.291
And where you saw your angel
that looked like Matt Damon.

36:33.292 --> 36:35.582
- Tell me more.
- Hi. Sorry.

36:35.583 --> 36:39.041
It wasn't an angel. It
was... It was more of a light.

36:39.042 --> 36:40.749
We never agreed on an angel.

36:40.750 --> 36:42.207
Now, Jess.

36:42.208 --> 36:44.832
I really... Talk to the other
people before you come to me.

36:44.833 --> 36:46.541
We know you mostly
through your father,

36:46.542 --> 36:48.707
Shadow Education
Secretary, Chris Crichton.

36:48.708 --> 36:50.707
You should probably
talk to JJ because he...

36:50.708 --> 36:52.624
He is really interesting.

36:52.625 --> 36:54.666
I'm sure he is.

36:54.667 --> 36:56.666
I'm sure you're all fascinating.

36:56.667 --> 36:59.416
But, Jess, our sympathies
lie particularly with you

36:59.417 --> 37:02.860
because of the devastating
disappearance of your sister, Jennifer.

37:03.000 --> 37:05.832
