39:04.167 --> 39:07.445
Well, it was gonna be my car
when Jen went to university.

39:10.125 --> 39:11.981
Found the car.

39:12.500 --> 39:14.143
Didn't find her.

39:15.083 --> 39:17.271
You know, just... Just gone.

39:19.583 --> 39:22.269
Perhaps she learnt
how to be invisible.

39:23.333 --> 39:25.236
Must be tough.

39:26.542 --> 39:28.957
My dad organised this
nationwide search.

39:28.958 --> 39:31.457
He really, really
got into it, you know.

39:31.458 --> 39:33.066
Mum...

39:33.333 --> 39:36.268
