place where my sister disappeared.

41:27.375 --> 41:29.480
Hmm. Look.

41:29.875 --> 41:31.041
What?

41:31.042 --> 41:33.359
Swifts.

41:33.417 --> 41:36.019
You know my favourite
thing about swifts?

41:36.333 --> 41:38.624
They nest on the wing.

41:38.625 --> 41:41.145
They're born and then they're fed.

41:41.583 --> 41:43.457
And from the moment they
leave their birthplace,

41:43.458 --> 41:45.499
they don't come down for
two years until they're ready

41:45.500 --> 41:48.374
to create other baby swifts.

41:48.375 --> 41:50.444
Oh, my gosh.

41:52.625 --> 41:54.916
You're a birdwatcher.

41:54.917 --> 41:57.768
That's why you wanted to kill yourself.

42:00.417 --> 42:02.957
No, no, I understand now.

42:02.958 --> 42:05.624
- Oh, yeah?
- Yeah, yeah.

42:05.625 --> 42:07.398
Good, good.

