cancer, for a start.

53:01.125 --> 53:03.541
I'm going to go,
uh, use the restroom.

53:03.542 --> 53:05.499
Then you'd probably
want loads of money

53:05.500 --> 53:08.067
so that you could donate
it to Cancer Research.

53:08.292 --> 53:10.957
You know, other people
are allowed to be in pain.

53:10.958 --> 53:12.861
You know that, Jess?

53:17.292 --> 53:20.060
Hey, mis amigos ingleses.

53:20.458 --> 53:21.724
How are we doing tonight?

53:23.375 --> 53:24.874
No, it's... Just leave it.

53:24.875 --> 53:26.916
Peachy, Angelo. Peachy.

53:26.917 --> 53:29.271
Great. Keep drinking.

53:37.208 --> 53:39.195
You're sitting in my seat.

53:39.625 --> 53:41.249
What?

53:41.250 --> 53:45.207
Uh, I'd find another seat, but
you're also sitting on my shawl.

53:45.208 --> 53:47.277
Oh, shit, sorry.

53:48.542 --> 53:50.350
