53:56.458 --> 53:59.558
You know, I think I
recognise you from somewhere.

54:00.042 --> 54:01.684
Ah.

54:01.917 --> 54:04.934
Yeah, um... There's this thing...

54:05.625 --> 54:09.851
That may have been in the
papers a bit recently, so...

54:10.458 --> 54:12.610
No, that's not it.

54:16.625 --> 54:18.315
Are you in a band?

54:19.417 --> 54:21.106
- What?
- Yeah.

54:21.375 --> 54:23.082
- You supported Alt-J.
- Yeah.

54:23.083 --> 54:25.650
- Manchester Towers.
- Two years ago.

54:25.750 --> 54:27.582
It was the first time
we came to Britain.

54:27.583 --> 54:29.166
- You're the front man, right?
- Yeah.

54:29.167 --> 54:31.484
I remember loving your lyrics.

54:31.667 --> 54:36.059
Really? Yeah, wow! You
