54:36.208 --> 54:39.652
Adolescent shit mostly.

54:40.375 --> 54:42.541
Are you still serious about it?

54:42.542 --> 54:44.315
Er...

54:44.583 --> 54:46.916
I was. Now, not so.

54:46.917 --> 54:48.725
What's your name?

54:48.750 --> 54:50.357
JJ.

54:50.708 --> 54:52.666
Which stands for?

54:52.667 --> 54:56.641
Er... John Julius.

54:58.625 --> 55:01.082
Hi, John Julius.

55:01.083 --> 55:02.499
I'm Kathy.

55:02.500 --> 55:05.102
Hello, Kathy.

55:07.417 --> 55:09.143
Wow!

55:16.667 --> 55:20.041
This is brilliant! Yeah!

55:20.042 --> 55:22.124
- I love it. This is beautiful.
- Yeah.

55:22.125 --> 55:23.707
Beautiful!

55:23.708 --> 55:27.582
- Who's that?
- That is, uh, my uncle.

55:27.583 --> 55:29.957
Ah! I think I recognise him.

55:29.958 --> 55:32.207
Yeah. He's, uh...
He's vaguely famous.

55:32.208 --> 55:34.999
Ah, a failed musician with
a vaguely famous uncle.

55:35.000 --> 55:36.374
I am a lucky girl.

55:36.375 --> 55:37.874
I enjoy it all the time, Angelo.

55:37.875 --> 55:39.778
See you later, mate.

55:53.833 --> 55:55.707
- Come on, let's go!
- Go where?

55:55.708 --> 55:57.582
- We're going to go dance.
- No, no, no, I'm happy to watch.

55:57.583 --> 55:59.166
- No, no, come on.
- Martin, I don't...

55:59.167 --> 56:00.856
Come on!

56:21.833 --> 56:23.606
Whoa!

56:31.375 --> 56:35.435
- So, uh, you're out here on your own?
- Mmm-hmm.

56:36.583 --> 56:39.648
Other people just crowd it
and make it about themselves.

56:40.375 --> 56:42.041
So you're... You're
here with family?

56:42.042 --> 56:43.374
Your uncle and...

56:43.375 --> 56:48.561
Uh, yeah, a bit of
