56:49.750 --> 56:52.186
But you don't like them?

56:52.583 --> 56:54.957
I mean, you ran away
from them at the bar.

56:54.958 --> 56:57.999
No, it's just they
can be a little, um...

56:58.000 --> 57:01.314
- A little intense, you know?
- Mmm-hmm.

57:02.167 --> 57:05.398
And you don't like intense?

57:05.542 --> 57:07.859
No, uh...

57:07.917 --> 57:12.582
