talk because I'm intense.

57:12.583 --> 57:15.150
Good.

57:15.792 --> 57:18.207
Because if you're looking
for a neurosis-free girl,

57:18.208 --> 57:19.832
you're bang out of luck.

57:19.833 --> 57:21.666
- Oh, yeah?
- Yeah.

57:21.667 --> 57:23.499
- Really?
- Yeah, I...

57:23.500 --> 57:26.807
I once set fire to my hair
just to see what would happen.

57:27.875 --> 57:30.791
I was 10 and it
didn't improve my look.

57:30.792 --> 57:32.457
Oh, that's, that's nothing.

57:32.458 --> 57:37.707
When I was a kid, I jumped off our
roof just to see if I could hurt myself.

57:37.708 --> 57:41.999
And, um, yeah, I
broke my leg and I...

57:42.000 --> 57:43.291
I kind of liked it.

57:43.292 --> 57:45.291
OK, well, how's this for psycho?

57:45.292 --> 57:48.291
I carved my
ex-boyfriend's initials

57:48.292 --> 57:50.041
- into my left inner thigh...
- Ah...

57:50.042 --> 57:52.874
as a way of telling him that
no-one else would ever see there.

57:52.875 --> 57:54.861
- Beat that.
- Um...

57:55.042 --> 57:56.832
Easy. I...

57:56.833 --> 58:01.124
I recently told some
people that I had cancer

58:01.125 --> 58:04.166
to avoid telling
them the real reason

58:04.167 --> 58:07.101
